The Armadyl godsword ornament kit is obtained as a possible reward from master Treasure Trails. It can be attached to the Armadyl godsword, making it an Armadyl godsword (or).

Once attached, the ornamented item becomes untradeable, but the kit can be detached from the item and sold.

The '''Armadyl godsword ornament kit''' is obtained as a possible reward from [[Clue scroll (master)|master]] [[Treasure Trails]]. It can be attached to the [[Armadyl godsword]], making it an [[Armadyl godsword (or)]].

Once attached, the ornamented item becomes untradeable, but the kit can be detached from the item and sold.
